title: BRIEF-Cytosorbents Expands Its Partnership With Biocon To Launch Cytosorb In Malaysia
text: February 15, 2018 / 12:23 PM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Cytosorbents Expands Its Partnership With Biocon To Launch Cytosorb In Malaysia Reuters Staff Feb 15 (Reuters) - Cytosorbents: * CYTOSORBENTS EXPANDS ITS PARTNERSHIP WITH BIOCON TO LAUNCH CYTOSORB® IN MALAYSIA * CYTOSORBENTS CORP - ‍BIOCON HAS EXCLUSIVE RIGHTS TO DISTRIBUTE CYTOSORB IN MALAYSIA, WHERE CYTOSORB IS ALREADY REGISTERED​ * CYTOSORBENTS CORP - ‍FINANCIAL TERMS OF AGREEMENT WERE NOT DISCLOSED​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
